mesa
------------------------------------------
X11 OpenGL libraries

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.19-4
  libX11_6-1.0.0-1
  libXext6-1.0.0-1
  libXt6-1.0.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  cygwin-1.5.19-4
  binutils-20050610-1
  cygport-0.1.0-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-1
  gcc-g++-3.4.4-1
  make-3.80-1
  pkg-config-0.20-1
  sed-4.1.4-1
  glproto-1.4.3-1

Canonical website:
  http://xorg.freedesktop.org/

Canonical download:
  http://ftp.x.org/pub/X11R7.0/src/everything/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack mesa-6.5-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./mesa-6.5-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mesa-6.5-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mesa-6.5-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mesa-devel-6.5-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mesa-doc-6.5-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGL1-6.5-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLU1-6.5-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLw1-6.5-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOSMesa6-6.5-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

